2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper involves the use of 3D models and aerial imagery, which are commonly used in computer graphics. 
3. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper's approach of using SIFT flow and iterative optimization can be applied to robotics applications such as robot navigation and mapping. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the processing of multimedia data such as aerial imagery and 3D models. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper's approach involves the use of optimization techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning.
